720234f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - Houston Street (West)
720234f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, south from West Houston Street as photo-
graphed from the uptown ''El' platform. Shown are the tracks and
station of the 9th Avenue ''El'' obliterating details of the street
below. Buildings shown are on the west side of dreenwich Street.
These are mainly warehouses and lofts.
May 7, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
720234f-a.folder: Greenwich Street & Houston Street (West), Manhattan, NY

720235f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - Houston Street (West)
720235f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, at West Houston Street, showing details of
the 9th Avenue 'El'' station and tracks at this point. The photo-
grapher is standing on the downtown platform and is viewing east-
ward towards that one opposite. Demolition of this structure and
its appurtenances is shortly to occur.
June 7, 1940
Views 1,2,3
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTD VS
